<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .header {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            height: 50vh;
            background: url('/image/cbg.jpg') no-repeat center center/cover;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .overlay {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        }

        .header-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .header p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 10px auto;
        }

        .content {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="overlay"></div>
        <div class="header-content">
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <p>At Elevate Workforce Solution, we are committed to bridging the gap between top talent and leading employers. Our mission is to create a seamless job-seeking experience while helping businesses find the right candidates efficiently. With a focus on innovation, integrity, and inclusivity, we strive to build a workforce that drives success for both individuals and organizations.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Why Us?</h2>
        <p>We offer a user-friendly platform designed to simplify job searching and recruitment. Our advanced matching system ensures that candidates find roles tailored to their skills, while employers gain access to top-tier professionals. With a commitment to excellence, personalized support, and a growing network of opportunities, Elevate Workforce Solution is your trusted partner in career and talent development.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

